gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pacers 123, Warriors 111
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pacers defeated the Warriors, 123-111. Tyrese Haliburton recorded 26 points (4-8 3PM), 11 assists, and three blocks for the Pacers, with Pascal Siakam adding 25 points, 16 rebounds, and six assists in the victory. Stephen Curry tallied 25 points, 11 rebounds, and five assists for the Warriors in the losing effort. The Pacers improve to 40-31, while the Warriors fall to 36-33.
